                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Jyoti make ideal guardians for artifacts too dangerous to be left where those hungry for power might seize them. Only they know what items of myth and legend, long thought lost or destroyed, lie within their crystal vaults. They are unreliable guardians of religious artifacts, however, which usually disgust them."
            }
